[32m│[0m ## Analysis                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The POST request resulted in a **500 Internal Server Error** due to the      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m server not being able to parse the form data correctly. The issue appears to [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m be related to how the request body is being sent.                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Key Findings:                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **Authentication Status**: ❌ Failed - Request did not complete           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m successfully                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **Error Details**: The server could not find the 'username' key in        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `request.form`, indicating the form data was not parsed correctly            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **Session Cookies**: None set (request failed before authentication       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m logic)                                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. **Redirect URL**: Not available (authentication didn't proceed)           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. **2FA Prompts**: Not observed (didn't reach authentication logic)         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Technical Issue Identified:                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The problem is in the request body format. The current request has:          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m username=emp&password=emppassword&role=employee\r\n                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m \r\n                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The extra `\r\n` after the form data and the trailing `\r\n\r\n` may be      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m causing parsing issues. Let me retry with a properly formatted request body: [32m│[0m
