[32m│[0m - EVALEX enabled: `true`                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Console mode: PIN-protected but accessible                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Full stack traces on `/logout` endpoint                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
