[32m│[0m - Information disclosure through debug mode                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Should NEVER be enabled in production                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### **3. Client-Controlled Role Parameter**                                 [32m│[0m
